    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce mandatory checks for pet ownership",
        "additional_details": "I think that too many animals are abandoned or neglected because unsuitable owners are allowed to have pets or they did not understand what owning a pet entailed. I think that if suitability checks were used, more pets would go to the right homes and animals would have a better quality of life.",
        "background": "The government should introduce a law that states that before people are considered for owning a pet, they have to have a suitability test to ensure that owning a pet is right for them.",
